name: Reefscape
desc: Two alliances compete to score coral on the reef and algae in the net or processor. At the end of the match, robots can climb on a shallow or deep cage.

name: Crescendo
desc: Two alliances compete to score notes in their amp and speaker. At the end of the match, robots can climb on their stages and score a note in the trap.

name: Charged Up
desc: Two alliances compete to score cones onto pegs and cubes onto shelves. At the end of the match, robots can balance on their charge station.

name: Rapid React
desc: Two alliances compete to score cargo in the upper and lower hubs. At the end of the match, robots can climb on their monkey-bar-style hangar.

name: Infinite Recharge
desc: Two alliances compete to score power cells in their inner, outer, and bottom port, turning their control panel for extra points. At the end of the match, robots can climb on their generator switch.

name: Destination: Deep Space
desc: Two alliances compete to score cargo and hatch panels on their rocket and cargo ship. At the end of the match, robots can climb on their hab platform.

name: FIRST Power Up
desc: Two alliances compete to score power cubes on their switch and scale, exchanging some for power-ups. At the end of the match, robots can climb on their rungs.

name: FIRST Steamworks
desc: Two alliances compete to score gears in their airship and fuel in their boiler. At the end of the match, robots can climb aboard their airship by rope.

name: FIRST Stronghold
desc: Two alliances compete to score boulders in their towers while destroying their opponents' defenses. At the end of the match, robots can scale their opponent's tower.

name: Recycle Rush
desc: Two alliances compete to stack totes and cans, while littering their opponents with pool noodles.

name: Aerial Assist
desc: Two alliances compete to pass a large ball between partners and score it in their upper or lower goals.

name: Ultimate Ascent
desc: Two alliances compete to score discs in a variety of goals. At the end of the match, robots can climb on their pyramid.

name: Rebound Rumble
desc: Two alliances compete to score foam basketballs in their hoops. At the end of the match, robots can balance on their bridges.

name: Logo Motion
desc: Two alliances compete to score their logo pieces on the scoring grid. At the end of the match, robots can deploy minibots to climb their poles.

name: Breakaway
desc: Two alliances compete to score soccer balls in their goals. At the end of the match, robots can climb on their towers or other robots that have climbed on the tower.

name: Lunacy
desc: Two alliances compete to score moon rocks and super cells in their opponents' trailers with the help of the human players.
